our ironclad privacy protocols.

253
00:09:06,013 --> 00:09:07,915
Fine, I'll just
get a warrant.

254
00:09:07,948 --> 00:09:09,016
Good luck with that.

255
00:09:09,049 --> 00:09:10,784
I mean, how long
did it take the FBI

256
