268
00:09:44,718 --> 00:09:47,020
Oh.

269
00:09:47,054 --> 00:09:48,689
Hmm.

270
00:09:48,722 --> 00:09:49,923
Little better?

271
00:09:49,957 --> 00:09:51,224
