Ha, ha. Funny.

278
00:10:07,407 --> 00:10:08,776
Also dark.

279
00:10:08,809 --> 00:10:10,410
Right. Fair point.

280
00:10:10,443 --> 00:10:12,312
But it's cool.

281
00:10:12,345 --> 00:10:14,948
You know, being dark.

282
00:10:14,982 --> 00:10:16,383
