287
00:10:25,125 --> 00:10:28,195
Somewhere other than Hell.

288
00:10:28,228 --> 00:10:30,964
See, I've, um, I've learned

289
00:10:30,998 --> 00:10:34,267
that there are consequences
to my darkness.

290
00:10:34,301 --> 00:10:37,404
Really permanent ones,
as it turns out.

291
00:10:37,437 --> 00:10:41,241
And I was thinking
you could help me avoid them?

292
00:10:41,274 --> 00:10:42,075
No way, José.

293
00:10:42,109 --> 00:10:45,345
