forensic thing.

302
00:11:03,897 --> 00:11:05,232
Yeah, yeah. See?

303
00:11:05,265 --> 00:11:07,901
Cray-cray.

304
00:11:07,935 --> 00:11:10,904
Well...

305
00:11:10,938 --> 00:11:12,105
I'm just gonna...

