some good news, you guys.

367
00:13:04,151 --> 00:13:06,920
He used the app to RSVP
for a mixer at Top Meet.

368
00:13:06,954 --> 00:13:08,021
It's happening tonight.

369
00:13:08,055 --> 00:13:09,122
