378
00:13:21,601 --> 00:13:23,303
Mm-hmm.
That's never stopped me
before, Daniel.

379
00:13:23,336 --> 00:13:25,906
I'm so good at flipping men,
they call me The Skillet.

380
00:13:25,939 --> 00:13:27,140
Oh, wow.
Okay.

381
00:13:27,174 --> 00:13:28,909
We need a woman, so I'll go.

382
00:13:28,942 --> 00:13:32,112
